LadyBlackArachnia,

If you just compare the file names then yes, they are all there, but if you actually WATCH them you will find that a few episodes of season 6 are there twice but under different names. 

For example, if you open the file named as "Season 6, Episode 20 - The Choice", it is the same episode as  "Season 6, Episode 21 - Baggage". The same for eps 16 and 17, and 12 and 13, meaning that 3 episodes are missing. Plus the first file of season 6 is actually "Broken" parts 1 AND 2, therefore the episode names for each following files are displaced.

If you don't actually watch them and just go by filenames then you can't see the problem, that was my (and a few other posters') point.
